title: [X-Plane] 50 X-Plane 11 Aircraft
description: Hi, here's 50 random aircraft that I've gathered from around the internet in the past 6 months. Not all of them are working, because I just keep on downloading new stuff and don't remember which ones are incompatible (I just compressed my xplane11/aircraft folder and uploaded it) list of the aircraft can be found here https://pasteboard.co/GAbvl99.png now, have fun, and when one of them doesn't work remember that I gave them to you for free, so don't complain! (p.s. this is a reupload of my previous one, the previous one wasn't working because I'm new to this stuff. anyway, please seed!)
